data.description: Location Location Location You will not want to miss this charming 3 bedroom 2 bath home with a full unfinished basement , perfect for a teen studio or in law suite, basement also has a 1 car garage and a separate entrance, this home is located only minutes from Jacksonville schools , home is located on a large corner lot , with access to Ladiga walking and biking trails , large back deck just off the kitchen great for backyard barbecues and entertaining. Partial back yard is fenced in , great for pets or gardens , don’t miss this one , it will not last long , located in a Kaitlin Court subdivision.
